snippet.title: Fire Emblem: Monshou no Nazo, Chapter 1, Book 1, Part 1
snippet.description:
I plan to do a playthrough of Fire Emblem: Monshou no Nazo. It won't quite be a LP, because I don't have a microphone and don't want my voice heard on the internet. Anyway, I'll probably end up doing both BK1 and BK2, with annotations to expain anything that I think needs explaining.

If you have any questions, comments, suggestions, etc, you can put them in the comments section, unless they have a possible spoiler for the game, in which case you'd be better off PMing me.
